Name: Precipice Blades
Effect: Target All Foes in Range. Low Accuracy 2. Ranged. Lethal. Unique. Ignore the Target's immunity to Ground-Type Damage. If a Target is Out of Range due to using a Move, this Move hits anyways.
Description: Giant blades emerge from the earth, impaling the unlucky souls nearby. Do you think you are safe in the air? Think again...
